replies.body:
Well, she does have good burst damage. LeBlanc is a hyper mobile assassin that is a lane bully, while able to instagib someone extremely quickly. The downside is that unlike other assassins, once late game comes around, she falls off extremely quickly. Also, she is getting a mini-rework rather soon, so keep that in mind. 

But I'm keen on {{champion:103}}

What exactly are you looking for besides "burst damage"? That would help the forum give out good suggestions that would fit your personality/playstyle.
